snippet.title: Sun Haven Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Sun Haven is set to release on Friday, June 25th, 2021! 

Wishlist us on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/14...
Support us on Indiegogo:  https://igg.me/at/sunhaven/x/25026515#/
Join our Discord: https://discord.com/invite/BqTCygE

Sun Haven is a relaxing farming simulation game that offers RPG gameplay for anyone who wants a little more adventure in their farm sim life. You can focus on farming and relationships with townsfolk, or go on an epic quest of magic and monsters. Or better yet – both!
